<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>They were the most comfortable couple in town last night during the 72nd Primetime Emmy Awards.</p>

<p>Gabrielle Union rocked a plus white bathrobe and shower cap as she presented Insecure from her home on Sunday night.</p>

<p>The 47-year-old actress looked fresh-faced while she joked about launching her rap career as she sang a few lines for the virtual show. </p>

