<p>Blessed: Unlike the usual hustle and bustle of prep for an awards show, Gabrielle enjoyed a relaxing day by the pool</p>

<p>'And I'm confident that the wheels of change are turning faster, and we'll reach an amicable agreement. 'I will never regret speaking up. Ever. Never ever.'</p>

<p>Gabrielle was fired from the NBC program for speaking out on racial insensitivity and working in a toxic culture. </p>

<p>She told Naomi that looking back on her career in Hollywood thus far, she's struck by 'the anti-blackness of it all,' which she called 'jarring and shocking, and it still is.</p>

<p>'There's a very narrow idea of what kind of black girl was acceptable and marketable.'</p>

<p>Unlike the usual hustle and bustle of prep for an awards show, Gabrielle enjoyed a relaxing day by the pool on Sunday.</p>

<p>She credited manicurist Thuy Nguyen for her nails and mentioned her own Flawless by Gabrielle Union hair care products while soaking up the sun.  </p>

